  </sponsors>
  <source>Gynuity Health Projects</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study examined the acceptability and feasibility of using a simplified regimen of
      medical abortion in Armenia and Azerbaijan. It was hypothesized that home use of mifepristone
      and misoprostol, and buccal administration of misoprostol, would be both acceptable to women
      and efficacious.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
